        Apparel
        Is Available!

        Check out the Dojo apparel in our team shop including sweatshirts and more!

        LEARN MORE

        Committed to Your Success

        Our focus is on your success and we accomplish this through exercise, self-discipline, respect and positive reinforcement. We have developed a unique program, teaching those skills that can be used to improve your health, confidence, and concentration as well as self-defense.

        LEARN MORE

        family, fun & Fitness

        Dojo Karate is passionate about families participating in this great sport together. Each of our programs are uniquely designed to fit the specific needs of the students in that group. Our classes cater to all ages and skill levels. Remember, a family that kicks together, sticks together!

        LEARN MORE

        PARTNERS IN EDUCATION

        Participating in Martial Arts is not only beneficial to your health and well-being, it will also affect other areas in your life. We find that the respect, motivation, dedication and focus that we instill into our students gives them the tools for success in karate, school, and life.

        LEARN MORE

        become a CHAMPION IN LIFE

        The Dojo Karate programs combine fitness and character development skills to create students that will succeed athletically and in all of their other endeavors. We show them how goal setting, healthy competition and hard work can aid in bully prevention and ensure success.

        LEARN MORE

        achieve your fitness goals

        Dojo Karate is passionate about helping students of all ages and abilities reach their fitness goals. We offer classes focused on martial arts, kickboxing and sport-specific resistance training both in and outside our schools. Are you interested in furthering your fitness level? Visit Dojo Karate today.

        LEARN MORE
        Find a Location

        We have 7 locations throughout the Minneapolis area.

        View Locations

        Training Programs

        You will begin by learning basic stances, kicks and punches. Working at your own pace, your body will adjust to regular exercise and you will begin gaining flexibility. Eventually you will be challenged with more and more advanced techniques. You will learn forms, combinations, and self-defense moves and more at every level.

        PreSchool / Kindergarten

        Approximately 3 to 5 Years

        At this young age, Dojo is dedicated to help our young students develop basic skills that both parents and children can be proud of.

        LEARN MORE

        Junior

        Approximately 5 to 10 Years

        To aid each student in succeeding in Karate and in school, we show them how focus, dedication and hard work will lead to positive results.

        LEARN MORE

        Pre-Teen

        Approximately 10 to 13 Years

        These classes will each continue to learn more detailed and skilled versions of one-steps, self-defense movements, combinations and forms.

        LEARN MORE

        Teenagers & Above

        Approximately 13 Years and Older

        At this point we aim for each student to excel in their Karate skills, potentially even participating in local, national or international competitions.

        LEARN MORE

        Ground Self-Defense

        Junior Level and Above

        This program will show our students how to defend themselves if they find themselves on the ground during an altercation.

        LEARN MORE

        Kickboxing

        Junior Level and Above

        Our kickboxing classes are designed to take sparring to the next level while furthering each student's fitness level and cardio goals.

        LEARN MORE

        Youth & Sport Training

        All Ages

        This program helps our students gain an overall confidence in what their body can do while giving them skills they can apply to other sports and activities.

        LEARN MORE

        Character Development

        All Ages

        This discussion based class focuses on leadership, sportsmanship, community involvement and the attitude of gratitude.

        LEARN MORE

        Team Evolution

        All Ages

        Team Evolution is designed for our students of all ages and skill levels to participate as a team in martial arts competitions.
